<Header HeaderType="HeaderTypes.H4">Navbar Link</Header>

<Paragraph>
    Navbar also uses the 'NavbarLink' subcomponent which can only be used inside it,
    this is meant for compatibility with the color configuration you do when you set up your project.
    NavbarLink knows which is the background color used by Navbar to be able to adjust automatically so that there are no color clashes.
    But if the default is not what is intended, it can be overriden so that it uses a different background color as base.
</Paragraph>

